  "title": "HR Transformation Manager (Gov Healthcare, RPA exp, Good Working Environment) #HCL",
  "description": "<ul><li>Identify and lead opportunities to streamline and enhance HR processes through automation</li><li>Develop solutions using automation tools to reduce manual workload</li><li>Design and implement solutions for smarter HR operations</li><li>Explore to elevate HR service delivery</li><li>Lead end-to-end transformation projects — from ideation to execution</li><li>Advocate for digital transformation and build capability across HR teams</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in Robotic Process Automation</li><li>3–5 years of experience in HR, automation, or process improvement</li><li>Degree in any field — we value practical ability and mindset over specific disciplines</li></ul><p><br />If you are interested in the position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to kaileylee@recruitexpress.com.sg<br /></p><p>Kailey Lee Jia Yueh</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24126040</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)</p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
